Tags:
  - Invocation=The Universal Elixir
  - Invocation=The Dispeller of Sin
By: Swami Ramdas
---
People do not know what the Name of God can do. Those who repeat it constantly
alone know its power. It can purify our mind completely. No other Sadhana
can do that. While the other Sadhanas can take us only to a certain stage,
the Name can take us to the summit of spiritual experience.
